🌎 INTRODUCING: The Lonely Planet Correspondent Network 🌏

We built a global collective of passionate travelers to share on-the-ground insights, stories and firsthand perspectives across social media – aka real people doing real things in the real world.

These creators, hand-selected by our social team, represent over 20 destinations and areas of expertise. They lead with curiosity, empower others to explore the world on their own terms and share our longstanding commitment to respectful, responsible travel. Link in bio to learn more, but in the meantime…

